        "original": "チャンスを待ったら一日千秋",
        "english": "Longing for a day waiting for a chance",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "02:52.550",
        "end": "02:54.150",
        "original": "追いかければ 東奔西走",
